---
import logo from '../../images/dog.jpg';
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
---

<section class="container mx-auto mt-4 gap-8 p-4 lg:mt-40">
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-4 lg:grid-cols-2 xl:gap-40">
    <div class="my-auto lg:pe-6">
      <h1 class="mb-8 text-2xl font-bold leading-tight xl:text-5xl">
        Your Local<span class="text-2xl font-bold leading-tight text-sky-900 xl:text-5xl"> Pet Care</span> Specialist
      </h1>
      <h2 class="xl:text2xl pb-8 text-xl font-bold leading-tight">Serving the Southern Highlands since 2019</h2>
      <div class="relative w-full cursor-pointer rounded-2xl sm:w-auto">
        <p class="text-xl">
          Welcome to our pet-loving hub in Hill Top, serving the Southern Highlands and Wollondilly areas! üêæ We specialize in drop-in pet care
          services, offering high-quality and affordable options. From quick check-ins to playful doggy adventures, we're here to make your pets' days
          brighter. Whether you're away for the day, need a break, or want some extra support, count on us for reliable drop-in care. Your pets'
          well-being is our top priority, ensuring they're happy and cared for in the comfort of their own home. Let us bring joy to your pets' day
          and peace to your mind!
        </p>
        <br />
        <p class="italic">Please note: We are not a boarding facility and do not offer this service.</p>
        <div class="pt-8">
          <button
            type="button"
            class="inline-block cursor-pointer select-none rounded border-[#5ad4f6] bg-slate-900 px-6 py-3 text-base font-medium text-white shadow-md shadow-gray-400
                       outline-none transition-all duration-500 hover:-translate-y-1.5 hover:bg-indigo-400 focus:outline-none focus:ring-0 focus:ring-offset-0">
            Get In Touch
          </button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div>
      <Image src={logo} alt="logo" class="float-end rounded-2xl" />
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
